                    <span>I've just read only section 2-1 (Manipulating Rightmst Bits) and I got much better understanding of binary arithmetic than I had before. As a collection of different computer arithmetic techniques the book is brilliant, but I think the book would have been even better if the auther had included derivations for formulas.</span>
                  
